<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<XMLConfigFile xmlns:xsd='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema' xmlns:xsi='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance'>

---Rift.NET Reloaded Emulator Configuration File---


----------------------------------------------------------------------
Realm Server Connection Settings
- RSPort = xxx; Default: 9100
- RSHost = xxx; Default: 127.0.0.1
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<RSHost>127.0.0.1</RSHost>
<RSPort>9100</RSPort>
<RealmName>Alpha Test Realm</RealmName>


----------------------------------------------------------------------
MiddleMan Server Connection Settings
- MMPort = xxx; Default: 9090
- MMHost = xxx; Default: 127.0.0.1
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<MMHost>127.0.0.1</MMHost>
<MMPort>9090</MMPort>


----------------------------------------------------------------------
World Server Connection Settings
- WSHost = 127.0.0.1
- WSPort = 8086
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<WSHost>127.0.0.1</WSHost>
<WSPort>9100</WSPort>


----------------------------------------------------------------------
World Server Misc Settings
- ServerLimit = The maximum number of players allowed on the server
- SaveTimer = The time between character saves
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<ServerLimit>1</ServerLimit>
<SaveTimer>90000</SaveTimer>


----------------------------------------------------------------------
- LogType - The place were the server will display
- Your choices: COLORCONSOLE, FILE, CONSOLE
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<LogType>COLORCONSOLE</LogType>


----------------------------------------------------------------------
---Level of Logging to use (default is NETWORK)---
----------------------------------------------------------------------
- Messages with importance below this log level will not be logged
-      NETWORK                 -Network code debugging
-      DEBUG                   -Packets processing
-      INFORMATION             -User information
-      USER                    -User actions
-      SUCCESS                 -Normal operation
-      WARNING                 -Warning
-      FAILED                  -Processing Error
-      CRITICAL                -Application Error
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<LogLevel>NETWORK</LogLevel>


----------------------------------------------------------------------
---Additional configuration for selected LogType---
----------------------------------------------------------------------
-      COLORCONSOLE        -""
-      CONSOLE             -""
-      FILE                -"myfile" -> myfile-yyyy-MM-dd.log
----------------------------------------------------------------------
<LogConfig>myfile</LogConfig>

</XMLConfigFile>
